column5: The sunfire IS damaged.....  i think the word is Totaled!
Awesome stuff KevinEspecially liked the first pic, QUALITY!!
ya......i think my boat might just come out early this year seeing your pics haha! i normally wait for the ice to leave but im willing to help it leave with my boat to.
Nice trout Kev..
Good job Lloyd, nice fish!

Late ice calls for new matters.         Use your boat as an ice breaker , make a trail , cast in the trail of broken slush/ice chunks ............. repeat!       in the a.m.'s we only had a small channel..........at 5 p.m. we hand a small like size erea to fish!     now its 23:42 p.m.  and tommorow is specks...........   AT 5 A.M.    :worthy:
Nice , quick report . Love that first shot
that first shot should be in a magazine! Fantastic!
Sweet, belles grises!!! I'm heading out right now for some lakers and specks!!!
AHAHHA!  this ictuer is hands down the best picture iv ever seen . i mean look at the subject man , its perfect!    :worthy:

Nice pic that first one. Am gonna go check out some streams now. Enjoy.

Super report  First picture is truly wicked
Great stuff!

Nice fish

a sun fire could make it!
